value.title: Explore a Wildlife Sanctuary – Florida!
value.description: Discover the beauty of Florida’s wildlife with a visit to a dedicated sanctuary! You’ll have the chance to see alligators, birds, and other fascinating creatures in a natural setting. It’s a chance to learn about conservation and Florida’s unique ecosystem.  It's a really special experience.\
value.location: Various Sanctuaries throughout Florida - check out [link to a relevant resource, e.g., a Florida Wildlife Federation site]”,
